lead_paragraph: Defender Geoff Cameron, midfielder Kyle Beckerman and forward Chris Wondolowski will miss the United States' World Cup qualifiers against Mexico and Costa Rica because of injuries, and Tim Howard has regained the No. 1 goalkeeper's job.

headline.print_headline: Cameron to Miss World Cup Qualifiers; Howard No 1 Keeper
